{
  "texts": [
    "The content of this paper is organized as follows.",
    "In Section 2, we explain the time-domain data of LAMOST-MRS.",
    "In Section 3, we describe the detailed procedure of sample selection for the MRS time-domain spectra and sources of solar-like stars employed in this work.",
    "In Section 4, we describe the processing of MRS Hα line data and the measures employed in this work to quantitatively indicate the stellar Hα activity intensity and variability.",
    "In Section 5, we present the analysis results of the variability of Hα chromospheric activity of solar-like stars based on the MRS timedomain data."
  ]
}